    public class TimeoutHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.xml.ws.handler.soap.SOAPHandler<javax.xml.ws.handler.soap.SOAPMessageContext>
    Author:
    - Mike Sheliga 6.2.18 Randomly generates SOAPFaults on incoming handleMessage for sayHi routine. Service side handler that mimics a web service request timing-out for the sayHi web method only. Methods aside from the incoming handleMessage do not do anything except print that they have been called.
